<br>
FD isn't much of a factor.  Somehow I'm able to pull single mobs and solo them fine, and a full group has to train to zone 3 times an hour?  I only have to use FD when a group of people are making like Amtrak to the zoneline with their ravenous beasts and 10 gorangas.  Since I only use FD when trained by other people so don't say that the only reason I'm not pulling monster trains around the zone is because I can FD.<br>
<br>
As soon as I find out about a place far away from the zone with good fear kite pathing and fearable mobs to pull, I'm there.  Maybe it'll get slightly better in a couple months.  <br>
<br>
Then again, people still train zone-in in Seb, so my faith in human intelligence is kinda low.  Please don't say &quot;it's easy for you not to train zone-in in Seb, you can FD&quot; =P<br>
